Updated information in Netbank
.br
:DUTCH10
You have been given a user profile to SEB Denmark's online banking system
- Netbank - where you can manage your brokonto. Please log in to Netbank
from seb.dk/brokonto.
.sp
In order to log in you need a NemID, which is the Danish equivalent to
the Swedish Bank-ID. If you do not already have a NemID, we have ordered
one on your behalf and it will be sent to your home adress. Please note
that the temporary access code recieved with your NemID is only valid for
30 days. We therefore urge you to log in and change your temporary code as
soon as possible.
.sp
